trans-unit.source: Defines the methods called during contract generation that can be used to modify the generated code for an operation.
trans-unit.target: Definiuje metody wywołane podczas generowania kontraktu, który może służyć do modyfikowania wygenerowany kod do wykonania operacji.

trans-unit.source: Implement the IOperationContractGenerationExtension interface on an operation behavior (a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior?displayProperty=fullName> type) to enable you to modify the code generated when a contract or endpoint is compiled into code.
trans-unit.target: Zaimplementuj interfejs IOperationContractGenerationExtension na zachowanie operacji ( <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>typu) umożliwia modyfikowanie kodu generowane, gdy kontrakt lub punkt końcowy jest kompilowany do kodu.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IOperationBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> inserts a custom operation behavior into the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection during the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Zazwyczaj niestandardowych <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>wstawia zachowanie operacja niestandardowa do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kolekcji podczas wywołania <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName>lub <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Implement to modify the code document object model prior to the contract generation process.
trans-unit.target: Wdrożenie, aby zmodyfikować kod document object model przed proces generowania umowy.

trans-unit.source: Typically, a custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> inserts a custom operation behavior into the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection during the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Zazwyczaj niestandardowych <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>wstawia zachowanie operacja niestandardowa do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName>kolekcji podczas wywołania <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName>lub <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.OperationDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The GenerateOperation method is called once for each contract.
trans-unit.target: Metoda GenerateOperation jest wywoływana raz dla każdej umowy.

trans-unit.source: The working context that contains the <xref href="System.CodeDom"></xref> types necessary to modify the generated operation.
trans-unit.target: Kontekst pracy, który zawiera <xref href="System.CodeDom"> </xref> konieczne zmodyfikowanie operacji wygenerowane typy.
